    <refname>pklocalauthority</refname>
    <refpurpose>polkit Local Authority Compatibility</refpurpose>
  </refnamediv>

  <refsect1>
    <title>DESCRIPTION</title>
    <para>
      The polkit Local Authority no longer exists.  Existing configuration
      files are honored; see
      <citerefentry>
	<refentrytitle>pkla-admin-identities</refentrytitle>
	<manvolnum>8</manvolnum>
      </citerefentry>
      and
      <citerefentry>
	<refentrytitle>pkla-check-authorization</refentrytitle>
	<manvolnum>8</manvolnum>
      </citerefentry>
      for description of the configuration format.
    </para>
    <para>
      Unlike the original Local Authority implementation, <emphasis>ReturnValue</emphasis> keys are ignored because
      <citerefentry>
	<refentrytitle>polkit</refentrytitle>
	<manvolnum>8</manvolnum>
      </citerefentry>
      no longer supports the functionality.
    </para>
  </refsect1>

